1. *Odgovornost* mi je da obavim svoj posao na vreme. (My responsibility is to finish my job on time.)
2. Učenici su se međusobno podelili *odgovornosti* za pripremu predstave. (The students divided the responsibilities between each other for the preparation of the show.)
3. Direktor je preuzeo *odgovornost* za sve pogreške. (The director assumed the responsibility for all the mistakes.)
4. Pokazala je *odgovornost* prema svom poslu. (She showed responsibility towards her job.)
5. Oni moraju da preuzmu *odgovornost* za svoje postupke. (They have to take responsibility for their actions.)